Description: Provides a unified interface to summarize survey or weighted data, supporting binary, continuous, categorical, and multiple-choice variables. 
    Built on top of the 'survey' and 'Hmisc' packages, it includes robust handling of complex survey designs, weighted summaries, and confidence intervals or quantile-based summaries.
